requires: cygwin libhogweed2 libnettle4 
sdesc: "A cryptographic library that is designed to fit easily in more or less any context (utilities)"
ldesc: "Nettle is a cryptographic library that is designed to fit easily in more or less any context:
In crypto toolkits for object-oriented languages (C++, Python, Pike, ...), in applications
like LSH or GNUPG, or even in kernel space."
